    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    Parser element for unsigned integer literals.

    Simple usage examples:
    &gt;&gt;&gt; from dragonfly.parser import Parser
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser = Parser(UnsignedInteger())
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;0&quot;)
    0
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;1234&quot;)
    1234
    &gt;&gt;&gt; parser.parse(&quot;0001234&quot;)
    1234</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
